OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and bright start to the
OL,6,Fday in very light winds. Temperatures
OL,7,Fclimb to another very hot day for many
OL,8,Fwith extreme heat warnings in place.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FA clear and dry night to come
OL,11,Fwith some isolated showers in the far
OL,12,Fsoutheast. Slightly cooler in the
OL,13,Fwest, but still warm in the east.
OL,14,FFeeling muggy.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSaturday:FDry, bright and hot to start
OL,17,Fthe weekend. Staying very hot but
OL,18,Ftemperatures slightly down on recent
OL,19,Fdays.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
